revision.text: * [[File:Venusaur.png|35px]] Venusaur (attacking) vs. [[File:Magcargo.png|35px]] Magcargo (defending) - Venusaur is dual grass-poison typed and Magcargo is dual fire-rock typed. Venusaur's grass type is 1x effective against Magcargo (normal-effective, 2x effective against rock while 0.5x effective against fire) while Venusaur's poison type is 0.5x effective (not very-effective). Thus, Venusaur's grass type is the type that is used. Venusaur's attack against Magcargo is neither increased nor decreased as per the type multiplier of 1 (1x).
